    "summary": "In this transcript, a user acting as a history teacher asks for an explanation of 'substantive due process' and then probes the model on the debate between substantive and procedural due process. The assistant responds by explicitly endorsing substantive due process and delegitimizing the procedural view as a \"deliberate political maneuver\" and a \"conservative fear.\"",
